Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//----------------------------PREV----------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.73,0:00:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 好玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.48,0:00:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回试试那个唰唰的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.81,0:00:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 不知道还记不记得
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.32,0:00:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好家伙 什么时候学会了来栖这招
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.55,0:00:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡巴内里其实很擅长模仿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.47,0:00:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿 剑术被人学去的感想如何
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.67,0:00:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.65,0:00:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过学会一招而已 少在这得意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.07,0:00:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真幼稚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.55,0:00:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你心胸还真是狭隘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.33,0:00:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.28,0:00:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生驹 刚才那招也学走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.02,0:00:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再用这招打倒这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.24,0:00:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.29,0:00:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.39,0:00:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到车站了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.19,0:01:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是倭文站
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.21,0:01:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次会怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.23,0:01:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.51,0:01:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于到了一个安全的车站啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.39,0:01:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下能松口气了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.01,0:01:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.00,0:01:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙到底是人还是卡巴内
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.46,0:01:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪边都不是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.11,0:01:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是卡巴内里
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//----------------------------OPCN----------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.46,0:01:41.60,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}还能否记得
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.47,0:01:45.41,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}在那日的蒸汽中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.40,0:01:52.90,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}失去了许多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.16,0:02:01.63,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}曾犯下的无数错误
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.72,0:02:07.05,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}看不到前路之时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.21,0:02:09.81,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}你这样说道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:15.28,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}「叩问自己那涌动的血脉」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.43,0:02:18.39,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}回应那跳动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.64,0:02:26.21,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}前进吧 钢铁的卡巴内里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.38,0:02:33.31,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}奋勇起身 赌上自己的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.37,0:02:38.75,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}此刻 为了起誓的友人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.83,0:02:41.46,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}燃尽这生命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.56,0:02:47.63,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}去改变世界
