Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.30,0:03:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去面见这个车站的领主
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.69,0:03:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲铁城的整备就拜托各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.66,0:03:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.34,0:03:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.33,0:03:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菖蒲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.35,0:03:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大达铁已经没了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.35,0:03:14.41,note3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1124,983)}No more
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.69,0:03:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大达铁？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.27,0:03:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喷流弹使用的材料
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.48,0:03:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一种容易蒸汽化的金属
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.14,0:03:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以提高贯穿力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.23,0:03:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那能拜托你们去采购吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.14,0:03:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.38,0:03:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲铁城的维修部件也要补充吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.98,0:03:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.22,0:03:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还需要一些衣服和药物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.98,0:03:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是让我们在八号晚上出发
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.88,0:03:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八号 不就是明天吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.35,0:03:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那今天是七夕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.87,0:03:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能悠闲地去挂诗笺了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.72,0:03:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.38,0:03:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道吗 七夕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在诗笺上写下心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.32,0:03:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再挂在竹子上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.73,0:03:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想试试
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.03,0:03:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 不知道有没时间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.75,0:03:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,采购的钱也不知道够不够
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.78,0:04:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来庆祝七夕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.16,0:04:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱的话 就用这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.42,0:04:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菖蒲大人 这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.30,0:04:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能拜托你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.89,0:04:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.31,0:04:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一～二～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说了吗 今天是七夕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.95,0:04:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全忘了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.94,0:04:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说采购组会买竹子回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.76,0:04:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那得开始写诗笺了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.78,0:04:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「竹儿 摇摇」…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.97,0:04:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 太心急了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.69,0:04:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 不要乱动啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.23,0:04:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.46,0:04:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这颜色真好看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.99,0:05:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出来买衣服真开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.58,0:05:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔换换衣服 感觉也不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.65,0:05:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.88,0:05:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更何况你总是穿那么暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.88,0:05:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是喜欢才穿成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.80,0:05:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里分头行动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.03,0:05:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去整备工厂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.81,0:05:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.57,0:05:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.52,0:05:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无名 一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.57,0:05:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我对买东西一窍不通
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.09,0:05:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一群女人 会被人欺负的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.41,0:05:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 保镖师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.57,0:05:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太贵了 太贵太贵了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.39,0:05:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太贵太贵了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.44,0:05:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看这里都烂了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.30,0:05:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便宜点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.18,0:05:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便宜点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.28,0:05:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有更厚的了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:05:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么薄连三天都撑不到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.43,0:06:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些我全都买了 给个半价吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.41,0:06:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种小豆子还卖10文？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.25,0:06:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.10,0:06:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳅也在战斗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.67,0:06:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.60,0:06:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.54,0:06:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 那是烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.32,0:06:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在倭文七夕是要放烟花的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.06,0:06:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有烟花的话 就是说也有火药吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.02,0:06:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能分给我们一点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.18,0:06:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是可以 但你要拿来做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.72,0:06:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也许可以用作喷流弹的燃烧剂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.05,0:06:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喷流弹？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枪不好使了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.02,0:06:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧修好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.78,0:06:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.27,0:06:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忙完这边的事马上就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.60,0:06:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.10,0:06:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们先来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区蒸汽工匠要违抗武士吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.05,0:06:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他刚才可是在跟我说话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.69,0:06:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外来佬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.18,0:07:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干了什么啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.85,0:07:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管螺丝了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.22,0:07:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先解决我的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.02,0:07:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去捡起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.30,0:07:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乱丢的玩具要自己收拾好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.58,0:07:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你娘没教过你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.64,0:07:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姿势完全不对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.35,0:07:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我傍晚过来取
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.25,0:07:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前给我修好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.74,0:07:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟卡巴内相比 这些武士根本不算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.03,0:07:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.74,0:07:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 喷流弹就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.61,0:07:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您能听他说下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.50,0:07:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐你是甲铁城的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.21,0:07:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的父亲也在骏城上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.28,0:08:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那是同伴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 他在的那辆叫扶桑城
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.57,0:08:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不太了解其他骏城的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.85,0:08:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扶桑城已经被卡巴内吞噬了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.02,0:08:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巢刈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.34,0:08:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面的人都变成了卡巴内
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.15,0:08:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那样冲进了显金站
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.99,0:08:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就是从那里逃出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.85,0:08:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.05,0:08:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直等待永远都回不来的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才更残酷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.56,0:08:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少我希望有人告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.41,0:08:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.50,0:08:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都是骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.46,0:08:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲…可是说过…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.40,0:08:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.53,0:08:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.52,0:08:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想把你弄哭的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.18,0:08:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是擦干眼泪后才是关键
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.36,0:09:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟我们是不请自来的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.64,0:09:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里都缺粮食
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.85,0:09:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但居然连交涉的机会都不给…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.05,0:09:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们搞错了战斗对手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.31,0:09:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这话说的很像生驹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.20,0:09:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.07,0:09:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菖蒲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.59,0:09:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来…来栖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.03,0:09:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.30,0:09:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.87,0:09:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等会儿看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.07,0:09:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.59,0:09:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是要尽早交涉…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.41,0:09:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等一小会儿
