Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.57,0:09:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.25,0:09:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次拜会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.30,0:09:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是四方川家的菖蒲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.81,0:09:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是身为家老的山崎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.33,0:10:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是献给倭文大人的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.95,0:10:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的年轻蒸汽工匠制造的喷流弹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.19,0:10:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有故障就不好了 正在检查
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.23,0:10:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来栖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.37,0:10:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.72,0:10:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是何等威力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.49,0:10:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样卡巴内的心包膜也能击穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.61,0:10:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若您需要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.78,0:10:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,设计图也可以交给您
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.65,0:10:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.17,0:10:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,困难的时候要互相帮助不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.22,0:10:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明…明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.14,0:10:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我答应给你们提供食物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.69,0:10:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤者和病人的接收也能拜托您吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.95,0:10:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这是当然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.08,0:10:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家老大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.49,0:10:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四方川家的继承人还在等着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.96,0:10:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请长话短说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.85,0:10:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是将军家的五州巡捕小源太
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.96,0:11:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位曾是解放者的耳目
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.26,0:11:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下名叫榎久
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.12,0:11:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么狩方众会在…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.31,0:11:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在他是我们的手下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.01,0:11:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解放者马上会到达倭文站
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.11,0:11:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.50,0:11:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中央的争斗与倭文无关
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.02,0:11:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少你脱不了干系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.17,0:11:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从十年前的那天开始…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.04,0:11:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.39,0:11:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看快看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.41,0:11:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买了这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.18,0:11:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 都装不下了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.62,0:11:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.48,0:11:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无名一背 就睡得很香呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.87,0:11:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.88,0:11:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.85,0:11:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.56,0:11:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳅给我买的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.20,0:11:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.10,0:12:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还弄到了这么漂亮的竹子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.25,0:12:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要用那个过七夕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.95,0:12:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.46,0:12:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在诗笺上写下心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.47,0:12:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后这样挂上去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.58,0:12:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.30,0:12:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去要好好装饰一番
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.10,0:12:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得来一次 不如在街上吃完再回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.34,0:12:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 这主意不错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.83,0:12:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.76,0:12:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无名呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.39,0:12:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才人还在的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.41,0:12:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙可没带「便当」出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.34,0:12:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.94,0:12:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便当？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.64,0:12:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.97,0:12:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你在这儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.76,0:12:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我找了好久
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.81,0:13:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.87,0:13:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘拿便当了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.86,0:13:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.54,0:13:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先说「我开动了」再喝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.93,0:13:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.24,0:13:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.85,0:13:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有庆祝过七夕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.91,0:13:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.37,0:13:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才看到竹叶又想了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.47,0:13:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.02,0:13:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈装饰着竹子说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.57,0:13:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Hozumi 今天放晴了真好 能看到银河呢」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.47,0:13:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hozumi？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.75,0:13:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.59,0:13:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到兄长大人之前的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.71,0:13:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么写呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.07,0:13:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.71,0:14:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能母亲是希望
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.81,0:14:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能吃米饭吃得饱饱的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.73,0:14:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才起了这个名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.54,0:14:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你笑什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.84,0:14:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说得好正经
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.69,0:14:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 肯定是这样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.03,0:14:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 妈妈还真是笨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.93,0:14:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大米什么的 明明早就不能种了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.37,0:14:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我们的食物…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.36,0:14:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我们现在还能这样聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.69,0:14:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定明天就会变成卡巴内
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.22,0:14:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可能就是今天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡觉的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.60,0:14:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总会想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.46,0:14:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等早上醒来的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.06,0:14:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是我自己吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.09,0:14:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心智说不定也会消失殆尽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.57,0:15:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样早上起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.07,0:15:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都会被我咬了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.70,0:15:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可怕的闹钟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.46,0:15:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.15,0:15:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你变回人类吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.31,0:15:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再跟卡巴内战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.81,0:15:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要抱着这种恐惧和卡巴内战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.01,0:15:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把你变回人类
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.56,0:15:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 如你母亲所希望的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.89,0:15:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你吃米饭吃到饱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.78,0:15:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那个…你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.53,0:15:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连如何变回人类都不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.80,0:15:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 吃米饭也就意味着要种田
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.67,0:15:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 要消灭所有卡巴内才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.55,0:15:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以两边都要做到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.60,0:15:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.98,0:15:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管哪一边都很难
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.67,0:15:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我已经决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.34,0:15:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你变回人类
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.31,0:16:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 如果不再是卡巴内里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.16,0:16:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不能战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.86,0:16:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.55,0:16:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡巴内都消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.26,0:16:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.29,0:16:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.47,0:16:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 大达铁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.66,0:16:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.38,0:16:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.30,0:16:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的刀可不是用来做这种事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.73,0:16:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你写了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.08,0:16:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 喂 别看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.31,0:16:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.87,0:16:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.68,0:16:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「希望能活下来」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.92,0:17:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在所能祈求的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.95,0:17:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是这种事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.07,0:17:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我也写好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.75,0:17:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的愿望是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.52,0:17:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「消灭卡巴内 夺回全部田地和车站」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.46,0:17:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 你这也太贪心了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.75,0:17:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那巢刈你只要活着就可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.70,0:17:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.52,0:17:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了活下去我还有更多愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.60,0:17:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要去实现
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.09,0:17:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也写好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.82,0:17:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的愿望是「复兴显金站」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.92,0:17:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.56,0:17:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 家主大人也一定会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.07,0:17:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.63,0:17:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.11,0:17:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦想就应该远大一些
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.80,0:17:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,处在这个时代更应如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.72,0:17:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我要变成有钱人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.96,0:18:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后娶三个漂亮老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.15,0:18:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三个？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.10,0:18:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说梦想就应该远大吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.37,0:18:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想成为私塾老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.28,0:18:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侑那写了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.49,0:18:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想拥有一辆自己的骏城
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.71,0:18:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让我也坐坐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.47,0:18:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来栖写了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.16,0:18:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菖蒲大人 不能看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.64,0:18:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果被看到 愿望就不能实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.69,0:18:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.25,0:18:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的愿望都让大家看过了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.77,0:18:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.89,0:18:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无名写了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.37,0:18:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃米饭吃到饱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.07,0:19:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄长大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.57,0:19:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.19,0:19:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家对我都很好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.72,0:19:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个兄长大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.55,0:19:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你舍弃「穗积」这个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.29,0:19:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还告诉你「弱者只有死路一条」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.53,0:19:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是这样的话 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.34,0:20:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是狩方众
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.99,0:20:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解放者大人万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.54,0:20:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人是什么来头
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.01,0:20:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狩方众
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.39,0:20:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为消灭卡巴内而组建的独立部队
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.84,0:20:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对卡巴内连战连胜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.56,0:20:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们所到之处卡巴内都被一扫而光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.64,0:20:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土地再次回到人类之手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.90,0:20:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是美马大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.16,0:20:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是何等英姿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.64,0:20:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是 将军大人的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.95,0:20:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄长大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.84,0:20:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无名
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.11,0:20:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于见到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.57,0:20:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.12,0:20:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄长大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.15,0:20:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无名的兄长大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.97,0:20:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是美马大人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.38,0:20:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就你一个人吗 四文呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.37,0:20:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在显金站被卡巴内袭击…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.54,0:20:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他死得很壮烈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.79,0:20:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.06,0:20:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿他轮回来世有所福报
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.33,0:21:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 你没事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.96,0:21:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 兄长大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.45,0:21:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有很多话想跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.95,0:21:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在甲铁城里…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.61,0:21:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须要确认一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.41,0:21:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他到底是不是真的英雄
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//----------------------------EDCN----------------------------
