Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.69,0:21:44.71,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}皆是同样被雨淋湿的梦境
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.75,0:21:47.62,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}只待干涸的光芒
