Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.41,0:22:14.73,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}呐喊与梦想皆已破碎 理想徒留其表
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.80,0:22:20.40,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}即便身溺俗世杂音之中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.46,0:22:25.98,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我仍将高歌 抛却方向之舵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.02,0:22:32.52,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}所以此刻的沉寂 只为让警钟回荡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.09,0:22:40.89,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Don't be afraid daybreak has come
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.57,0:22:46.67,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Don't be afraid daybreak has come
