Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.28,0:17:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\b0\fs50\shad0\blur2}Some little ironies
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.63,0:17:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\b0\fs50\shad0\blur2}Call tragedies so silently
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.94,0:17:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\b0\fs50\shad0\blur2}And you faced their gravity
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.34,0:17:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\b0\fs50\shad0\blur2}In agony, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.84,0:17:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\b0\fs50\shad0\blur2}Don't be afraid
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.23,0:17:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\b0\fs50\shad0\blur2}The daybreak has come out
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.31,0:17:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\b0\fs50\shad0\blur2}There's no curtain call
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.29,0:17:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\b0\fs50\shad0\blur2}No regrets are needed
